      (Bruce Momjian)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在<application>pg_upgrade</>中，在处理之前，检查不适当的非可连接数据库
 (Bruce Momjian)
</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      In <application>pg_upgrade</>, quote directory paths
