      (Bruce Momjian)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在<application>pg_upgrade</>中，在生成的<literal>delete_old_cluster</>
脚本中正确的引用目录路径 (Bruce Momjian)
</para>
    </listitem>    
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      In <application>pg_upgrade</>, preserve database-level freezing info
      properly
      (Bruce Momjian)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在<application>pg_upgrade</>中，适当的保护数据库级别的冻结信息 (Bruce Momjian)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This oversight could cause missing-clog-file errors for tables within
