这会导致瞬间的错误回复或查询失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Avoid flattening a subquery whose <literal>SELECT</> list contains a
      volatile function wrapped inside a sub-<literal>SELECT</> (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
避免压缩一个<literal>SELECT</>列表中包含一个包含在子<literal>SELECT</>
中的不稳定函数的子查询 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This avoids unexpected results due to extra evaluations of the
      volatile function.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这避免了由于额外评估该不稳定函数引起的意外结果。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix planner's processing of non-simple-variable subquery outputs
      nested within outer joins (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复规划器对非简单变量子查询输出嵌套在外连接中的处理 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This error could lead to incorrect plans for queries involving
      multiple levels of subqueries within <literal>JOIN</> syntax.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个错误会导致在<literal>JOIN</>语法中包含多级别子查询的查询的错误规划。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix premature deletion of temporary files (Andres Freund)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复临时文件的过早删除 (Andres Freund)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible read past end of memory in rule printing (Peter Eisentraut)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复规则打印中可能读取过去的内存 (Peter Eisentraut)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix array slicing of <type>int2vector</> and <type>oidvector</> values
      (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<type>int2vector</>和 <type>oidvector</>值的数组切片 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Expressions of this kind are now implicitly promoted to
      regular <type>int2</> or <type>oid</> arrays.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这种类型的表达式现在隐式的转换成普通的<type>int2</>或<type>oid</>数组。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect behaviors when using a SQL-standard, simple GMT offset
      timezone (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复使用SQL标准、简单GMT偏移时区时的错误行为 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      In some cases, the system would use the simple GMT offset value when
      it should have used the regular timezone setting that had prevailed
      before the simple offset was selected.  This change also causes
      the <function>timeofday</> function to honor the simple GMT offset
      zone.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在某些情况下，系统会在它应该使用在简单偏移被选择之前盛行的常规时区设置时，
使用了简单GMT偏移值。这个修改也使<function>timeofday</>
函数遵守简单GMT偏移时区。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent possible misbehavior when logging translations of Windows
      error codes (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在记录Windows错误代码的翻译时阻止可能的错误行为 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Properly quote generated command lines in <application>pg_ctl</>
      (Naoya Anzai and Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在<application>pg_ctl</>中正确的引用生成的命令行 (Naoya Anzai and Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This fix applies only to Windows.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个修复仅适用于Windows。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>pg_dumpall</> to work when a source database
      sets <link
      linkend="guc-default-transaction-read-only"><varname>default_transaction_read_only</></link>
      via <command>ALTER DATABASE SET</> (Kevin Grittner)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<application>pg_dumpall</>，使其在源数据库通过<command>ALTER DATABASE SET</>
设置<link linkend="guc-default-transaction-read-only"><varname>default_transaction_read_only</></link>
时工作 (Kevin Grittner)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Previously, the generated script would fail during restore.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前，生成的脚本在恢复期间会失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s processing of lists of variables
      declared <type>varchar</> (Zolt&aacute;n B&ouml;sz&ouml;rm&eacute;nyi)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<application>ecpg</>对<type>varchar</>声明的变量列表的处理
 (Zolt&aacute;n B&ouml;sz&ouml;rm&eacute;nyi)
</para>
    </listitem>    
    
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make <filename>contrib/lo</> defend against incorrect trigger definitions
      (Marc Cousin)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让<filename>contrib/lo</>防卫不正确的触发器定义 (Marc Cousin)
</para>
    </listitem>    
    
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2013h
      for DST law changes in Argentina, Brazil, Jordan, Libya,
      Liechtenstein, Morocco, and Palestine.  Also, new timezone
      abbreviations WIB, WIT, WITA for Indonesia.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2013h，
因为DST规律在Argentina、Brazil、Jordan、Libya、Liechtenstein、
Morocco和Palestine发生了改变。另外，Indonesia
的新时区缩写WIB、WIT、WITA。
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-9-0-14">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 9.0.14</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>版本 9.0.14</title>

  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>2013-10-10</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>2013-10-10</para>
  </formalpara>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 9.0.13.
   For information about new features in the 9.0 major release, see
   <xref linkend="release-9-0">.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个版本包含各种自9.0.13以来的修复。想要获得关于9.0主版本的新特性信息，
请参阅<xref linkend="release-9-0">。
</para>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Migration to Version 9.0.14</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本 9.0.14</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 9.0.X.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
运行9.0.X的系统不需要转储/恢复。
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    However, if you are upgrading from a version earlier than 9.0.13,
    see <xref linkend="release-9-0-13">.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
不过，如果你是从一个早于9.0.13的版本升级而来，请参阅<xref linkend="release-9-0-13">。
</para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent corruption of multi-byte characters when attempting to
      case-fold identifiers (Andrew Dunstan)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
阻止尝试合并大小写标识符时多字节字符的损坏 (Andrew Dunstan)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      <productname>PostgreSQL</> case-folds non-ASCII characters only
      when using a single-byte server encoding.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
<productname>PostgreSQL</>仅在使用单字节服务器编码时合并大小写非ASCII字符。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix checkpoint memory leak in background writer when <literal>wal_level =
      hot_standby</> (Naoya Anzai)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<literal>wal_level = hot_standby</>时后台写作检查点内存泄露 (Naoya Anzai)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory leak caused by <function>lo_open()</function> failure
      (Heikki Linnakangas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>lo_open()</function>失败导致的内存泄露 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory overcommit bug when <varname>work_mem</> is using more
      than 24GB of memory (Stephen Frost)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<varname>work_mem</>使用超过24GB内存的内存过度使用错误 (Stephen Frost)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix deadlock bug in libpq when using SSL (Stephen Frost)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复使用SSL时libpq中的死锁错误 (Stephen Frost)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible SSL state corruption in threaded libpq applications
      (Nick Phillips, Stephen Frost)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复线程libpq应用程序中可能的SSL状态损坏 (Nick Phillips, Stephen Frost)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Properly compute row estimates for boolean columns containing many NULL
      values (Andrew Gierth)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
适当的计算包含许多NULL值的布尔字段的行估计 (Andrew Gierth)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Previously tests like <literal>col IS NOT TRUE</> and <literal>col IS
      NOT FALSE</> did not properly factor in NULL values when estimating
      plan costs.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前的文本，像<literal>col IS NOT TRUE</>和<literal>col IS NOT FALSE</>，
在估计规划开销时并不能适当的包括进NULL值中。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent pushing down <literal>WHERE</> clauses into unsafe
      <literal>UNION/INTERSECT</> subqueries (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
阻止将<literal>WHERE</>子句下推到不安全的<literal>UNION/INTERSECT</>子查询中 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Subqueries of a <literal>UNION</> or <literal>INTERSECT</> that
      contain set-returning functions or volatile functions in their
      <literal>SELECT</> lists could be improperly optimized, leading to
      run-time errors or incorrect query results.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
<literal>SELECT</>列表中包含设置返回函数或不稳定函数的<literal>UNION</>
或<literal>INTERSECT</>的子查询会被不适当的最优化，导致运行时错误或不正确的查询结果。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix rare case of <quote>failed to locate grouping columns</>
      planner failure (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<quote>failed to locate grouping columns</>规划器失败的罕见情况 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve view dumping code's handling of dropped columns in referenced
      tables (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
提高视图转储代码对引用表中被删除的字段的处理 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Properly record index comments created using <literal>UNIQUE</>
      and <literal>PRIMARY KEY</> syntax (Andres Freund)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
适当的记录用<literal>UNIQUE</>和<literal>PRIMARY KEY</>语法创建的索引注释 (Andres Freund)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This fixes a parallel <application>pg_restore</> failure.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这修复了一个并行的<application>pg_restore</>错误。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <command>REINDEX TABLE</> and <command>REINDEX DATABASE</>
      to properly revalidate constraints and mark invalidated indexes as
      valid (Noah Misch)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复了<command>REINDEX TABLE</>和<command>REINDEX DATABASE</>，
以正确的使约束重新生效，并且标记无效的索引为有效 (Noah Misch)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      <command>REINDEX INDEX</> has always worked properly.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
<command>REINDEX INDEX</>总是正常工作。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible deadlock during concurrent <command>CREATE INDEX
      CONCURRENTLY</> operations (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复并发<command>CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY</>操作期间可能的死锁 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <function>regexp_matches()</> handling of zero-length matches
      (Jeevan Chalke)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>regexp_matches()</>处理零长度匹配 (Jeevan Chalke)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Previously, zero-length matches like '^' could return too many matches.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前，像'^'这样的零长度匹配可能返回很多匹配。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix crash for overly-complex regular expressions (Heikki Linnakangas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复过度复杂的正则表达式的崩溃 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix regular expression match failures for back references combined with
      non-greedy quantifiers (Jeevan Chalke)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复正则表达式逆向引用和非贪婪量词结合的匹配错误 (Jeevan Chalke)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent <command>CREATE FUNCTION</> from checking <command>SET</>
      variables unless function body checking is enabled (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
阻止<command>CREATE FUNCTION</>检查<command>SET</>变量，除非启用了函数体检查 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Allow <command>ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES</> to operate on schemas
      without requiring CREATE permission (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
允许<command>ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES</>在模式上操作，不需要CREATE权限 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Loosen restriction on keywords used in queries (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
放松了在查询上使用的关键字的限制 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Specifically, lessen keyword restrictions for role names, language
      names, <command>EXPLAIN</> and <command>COPY</> options, and
      <command>SET</> values.  This allows <literal>COPY ... (FORMAT
      BINARY)</> to work as expected; previously <literal>BINARY</> needed
      to be quoted.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
特别的，减少了角色名、语言名、<command>EXPLAIN</>和<command>COPY</>操作、
还有<command>SET</>值的关键字的限制。这允许<literal>COPY ...  (FORMAT
      BINARY)</>像预期的那样工作；以前的<literal>BINARY</>需要加引号。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <function>pgp_pub_decrypt()</> so it works for secret keys with
      passwords (Marko Kreen)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复了<function>pgp_pub_decrypt()</>，这样它为带有口令的秘钥工作 (Marko Kreen)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Remove rare inaccurate warning during vacuum of index-less tables
      (Heikki Linnakangas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
删除缺少索引的表vacuum期间稀有的不准确的警告 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that <command>VACUUM ANALYZE</> still runs the ANALYZE phase
      if its attempt to truncate the file is cancelled due to lock conflicts
      (Kevin Grittner)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
如果<command>VACUUM ANALYZE</>截断文件的尝试由于锁冲突而取消，
确保它仍然运行ANALYZE (Kevin Grittner)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Avoid possible failure when performing transaction control commands (e.g
      ROLLBACK) in prepared queries (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
避免在预备查询中执行事务控制命令时可能的错误（如 ROLLBACK） (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that floating-point data input accepts standard spellings
      of <quote>infinity</> on all platforms (Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保所有平台上浮点数据输入接受标准的<quote>infinity</>拼写 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The C99 standard says that allowable spellings are <literal>inf</>,
      <literal>+inf</>, <literal>-inf</>, <literal>infinity</>,
      <literal>+infinity</>, and <literal>-infinity</>.  Make sure we
      recognize these even if the platform's <function>strtod</> function
      doesn't.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
C99标准指出允许的拼写是<literal>inf</>、<literal>+inf</>、<literal>-inf</>、
<literal>infinity</>、<literal>+infinity</>和<literal>-infinity</>。
确保我们能够认出它们，即使该平台的<function>strtod</>函数不能认出。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Expand ability to compare rows to records and arrays (Rafal Rzepecki,
      Tom Lane)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
扩张比较行的能力到记录和数组 (Rafal Rzepecki, Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2013d
      for DST law changes in Israel, Morocco, Palestine, and Paraguay.
      Also, historical zone data corrections for Macquarie Island.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2013d，因为DST规律在Israel、
Morocco、Palestine和Paraguay方面改变了。另外，
Macquarie Island历史时区数据纠正。
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

